[Student "S"]
{NORTH has both Majors and planned on bidding 1\H first, (up-the-line). 
But WEST's overcall gave NORTH the opportunity to bid both Majors at the same time! Since the 
Negative Double promises both Majors it was like NORTH could bid 1\H\S.

SOUTH has \Ss so she bids 1\S, showing a minimum opener.

NORTH has 13 points and the \S fit so he bids game.}

